{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N tee Wilisteri karroja piht/ un atradde Saulu un\npretēt Israēlu/ un Isra-\netā Wiḣri behdse preeḱsch\nteem Wilistereem/ un kritte no-\nkauti us to Kalnu Gilboa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tee Wilisteri lausahs\nus Saulu/ un us winna Deh-\nleem/ un tee Wilisteri nokawe\nJonatanu/ un Abinadabu / un\nMalkisui/ Saula Dehlus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Kauschana bija bref-\nmiga prett Saulu/un tee Strehl-\nnekti aisnehme winnu ar favcem\nStohpeem/ ka winch no teem\nStrehlneekteem eewainohts ktua.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls us fa-\nwu Brukku- Netteju: Jswelz\ntawu Sobbinu/ un nodurr man\nar to/ ka schee Neapgraisiti ne\nnaht un mann Smectla leek. Bet\nwinna Brukku-Nettejs ne grib-\nbeja/ jo winch bihjajahs totti.\nTad nehme Sauls to Sobbinu/\nun mettehs us to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu winna Brukku-\nNettejs redseja/ ka Sauls bija\nnomirris/ tad mettehs winch ar-\nri Sobbinā/ un nomirre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta nomirre Sauls / un\nwinna trihs Dehli/ un wits win-\nna Nains nomirre koḣpā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad un wisfi Israēla Wiḣ-\nri/ kas Eeleijā bija/ redseja/ ka\ntee behdse/ un ka Sauls un win-\nna Dehli bija nomirruscht / tad\npamette tee jawus Pilsfahtus/\nun behdse/ un tee Wilisteri nah-\nze/ un dsihwaja eekfch teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ohtra Deena nahze tee\nWilisteri tohs Nokautus aplau-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "wizza Dehlus us Gilboas Kal-\nnu gullim/\n\nUn tee iswilke taim Dreh-\nbes/ un pazehle winna Galwit\nun winna Brukkaś/ un fuhtija\ntohs Wilisteru Seimmê apkahrt/\nka tas isteikts taptu jawu Elka-\nDeewu Namma/ un starp teem\nLaudim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee nolikke winna\nBrukkaś fawā Deewa Nam-\nmā/ un winna Galwu peekalle\ntee pee Dagoxa Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu wisfi Jabeṣā eekfch\nGileadas dsirdeja/ wiḣu/ ko tee\nWilisteri Saulam bij darrijschi/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs wisfi spehzi-\ngi Wiḣri/ un nehme Saula Mee-\nlas/ un winna Dehlu Meefas/\nun nehfe tahs us Jabeṭu/ un ap-\nrakfe winnu Raulus Jabeṣā ap-\npakfch to Obsolu/ un gaveja tep-\ntinas Deenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta nomirre Sauls eekfch\nfaweem Grehkrein / ko winch\nprett to KUNGU bij darrijs/ ta\nKUNGA Wahṛda pehz/ ko tas\nne turreja. Ir ka winch to Siḣ-\nneezi bij waizajs un meklejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ne bij to KUNGU wai-\nzajs/ tapehz nokawe winch to /\nun greese to Walstibu pee Dah-\nwidu Isaja Dehlu.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
